snippet.title: Total War: WARHAMMER 2 - Blood for the Blood God 2 Trailer
snippet.description:
The scarred lands run crimson with the arrival of the Blood for the Blood God Effects Pack for WARHAMMER 2.

Blood for the Blood God  is free for WARHAMMER II players who have already purchased Blood for the Blood God for the original Total War: WARHAMMER, or can be purchased on here: http://store.steampowered.com/app/594591

Once downloaded, Blood effects can be enabled in the Advanced Graphics Settings of Total War: WARHAMMER II.

For more information vist our FAQ: https://www.totalwar.com/blog/mortal-empires-patch-notes

For all the latest info, follow us on social media:
